Run:
 - build_vignette_news() for news
 - build_vignette_grammar() for an organized list of all functions
 - build_vignette_data.summary() for summary statistics about the population
 - build_vignette_errors() for multiple checks on the raw data
 - build_vignette_tutorial.ranks() for an old (not so great) tutorial
 - build_vignette_devel() for developer tips & guidelines
 - help(package = 'hyenaR') to access all help files

Tip:
 create_id_starting.table() is the best function to start most workflow. It is a very flexible, so check its documentation to discover how to customize all its arguments!
